{
  "stem": "16140.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then when I saw approaching the Nazi officers, we started to run.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they started to shoot after us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were running after us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then they returned, and they let us run away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Me, my mother, my aunt, my uncle, and neighbors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We run away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the first night, we stayed at-- at Polish-- at Polish people in a village on a hideout.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they started to burn villages where they were finding Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I decided we go to the woods. instead of staying with the Polish people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The woods was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was quite a miles away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Well, I mean, you just go to the woods that's all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, hours.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not a whole day, hours.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were begging food from the farmers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They give us food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes they give us work, like making sweaters and socks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, before the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans were in Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because when Hitler made a pact with Russia, all the German people went to Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was lots of Jewish people in the woods.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the Nazis used to come and look for Jewish people and kill them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember one time we were at-- at the hide out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the hide out was like you dug out a hole.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then on top, you put ground on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Nazis were standing on our ground.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was a little girl, my aunt's little girl started to cry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she started to choke her and wanted to kill her, because she was afraid the Nazis will find out our hide out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sonja.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One-year-old, two years old, something like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I didn't like my aunt to choke her to death.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
